NAME
    Pod::Weaver::Plugin::SubSpec - Insert POD for subs from spec

VERSION
    version 0.02

SYNOPSIS
    In your "weaver.ini":

     [-SubSpec]

DESCRIPTION
    This plugin inserts POD documentation (generated by Sub::Spec::Pod) at
    the end of the "=head1 FUNCTIONS" section. That section must already
    exist, or the file will be skipped.

SEE ALSO
    Sub::Spec::Pod

    Sub::Spec

    Pod::Weaver

